import React, { useEffect } from 'react' import { Navigate, useLocation, useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom' function AddResults() { const location = useLocation() const navigate = useNavigate() const {user, examinfo: {year, branch, heldin}, subjects: {sub1, sub2, sub3, sub4, sub5}} = location.state useEffect(()=>{ console.log(location.state) if(location.state == null ){ window.alert('Not logged in') navigate('/Teacher/Teacherlogin') } }) return (

Logged in as: {user}

Year: {year}

Branch: {branch}

Held in: {heldin}

{sub1}

{sub2}

{sub3}

{sub4}

{sub5}

) } export default AddResults
